        <mxCell id="ann_decompose" value="1. Decompose query → 1–N sub-questions&#xa;   (single-issue, no multi-hop)&#xa;2. Route each sub-question in parallel:&#xa;   confidence ≥0.9 → matched agencies only&#xa;   confidence &lt;0.9  → broadcast all agencies" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#d6b656;fillColor=#fffacd;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;fontSize=11;rounded=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
